interpretation: The "person feeding baby" card represents nurturing, caretaking, and selflessness. This card reminds us to prioritize the needs of others, especially those who are vulnerable and dependent on us. It encourages us to find joy in acts of service and to take on the responsibility of caring for those who cannot care for themselves. The "person feeding baby" card can also symbolize the importance of motherhood, family, and the bonds of love that connect us to one another. This card reminds us to be patient, kind, and gentle with ourselves and others as we navigate the challenges of caretaking. Keywords associated with this card include nurturing, caretaking, selflessness, motherhood, family, love, patience, and gentleness.
